	<article id="post-3852" class="post-3852 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-courage category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-machon category-media category-national-security category-privacy-2 category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-talks-2 category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-annie-machon tag-courage tag-edward-snowden tag-intelligence-2 tag-international-journalism-conference tag-media-2 tag-perugia tag-surveillance-2 tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/international-journalism-festival-perugia.html" title="Permalink to International Journalism Festival, Perugia" rel="bookmark">International Journalism Festival, Perugia</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/international-journalism-festival-perugia.html" title="19:56" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-05-10T19:56:08+00:00" pubdate>May 10, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/international-journalism-festival-perugia.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is a panel dis­cus­sion I did at the Inter­na­tional Journ­al­ism Fest­ival in Per­u­gia, Italy, in May 2014:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/scoop_century_placeholder.jpg" alt="scoop_century_placeholder" width="708" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3855" data-source="vimeo" data-id="99561640" /></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/international-journalism-festival-perugia.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/courage" title="View all posts in Courage" rel="category tag">Courage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/media" title="View all posts in Media" rel="category tag">Media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/wikileaks" title="View all posts in Wikileaks" rel="category tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/courage" rel="tag">Courage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/international-journalism-conference" rel="tag">International Journalism Conference</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/media-2" rel="tag">media</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/perugia" rel="tag">Perugia</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
