				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/annie-machon" rel="tag">Annie Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/bill-binney" rel="tag">Bill Binney</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chris-hedges" rel="tag">Chris Hedges</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chris-huhne" rel="tag">Chris Huhne</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/debate" rel="tag">debate</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/democracy-2" rel="tag">democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/edward-snowden" rel="tag">Edward Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/oxford-union-society" rel="tag">Oxford Union Society</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
