				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/chelsea-manning" rel="tag">Chelsea Manning</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/civil-liberties-2" rel="tag">civil liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/oxford-union-society" rel="tag">Oxford Union Society</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/saaii" rel="tag">SAAII</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sam-adams-award" rel="tag">Sam Adams Award</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/the-whistler" rel="tag">The Whistler</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/war" rel="tag">war</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistelblowers" rel="tag">whistelblowers</a>			</span>
						
