		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/01/ccc-talk-four-wars.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/courage" title="View all posts in Courage" rel="category tag">Courage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/cryptoparty" title="View all posts in Cryptoparty" rel="category tag">Cryptoparty</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/drugs-2" title="View all posts in Drugs" rel="category tag">Drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/law" title="View all posts in Law" rel="category tag">Law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi5" title="View all posts in MI5" rel="category tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi6" title="View all posts in MI6" rel="category tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/nsa" title="View all posts in NSA" rel="category tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/osa" title="View all posts in OSA" rel="category tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/politics" title="View all posts in Politics" rel="category tag">Politics</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/prohibition-2" title="View all posts in Prohibition" rel="category tag">Prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/talks-2" title="View all posts in Talks" rel="category tag">Talks</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/technology" title="View all posts in Technology" rel="category tag">Technology</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/wikileaks" title="View all posts in Wikileaks" rel="category tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/30c3" rel="tag">30C3</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/ccc" rel="tag">CCC</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/courage" rel="tag">Courage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/drugs" rel="tag">drugs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/mi5" rel="tag">MI5</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nsa" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/privacy" rel="tag">privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/prohibition" rel="tag">prohibition</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/snowden" rel="tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/terrorism-2" rel="tag">terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
